---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Accessibility Statement | Freedom Mobility NY"
  description="Our commitment to making our website and services accessible to everyone."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>Freedom Mobility NY is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience and applying relevant accessibility standards.</p>

    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We follow WCAG 2.1 AA guidelines where feasible.</li>
      <li>Our site uses semantic HTML, proper heading structure, ARIA labels, and sufficient color contrast.</li>
      <li>Images include meaningful alternative text.</li>
      <li>Forms are labeled and keyboard accessible.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Limitations</h2>
    <p>While we strive for full accessibility, some third-party content or older documents may not yet meet the highest standards. We are actively working to address these areas.</p>

    <h2>Feedback</h2>
    <p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of our website. Please let us know if you encounter any barriers:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@freedommobilityny.com">info@freedommobilityny.com</a></li>
      <li>Phone: (585) 488-0771</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We aim to respond to accessibility feedback within 5 business days.</p>

    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block mt-8 bg-slate-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl no-underline">Contact Us About Accessibility</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
```

Now update the footer links in Layout to point to the new real pages.